{"tid":1136832,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG]白卡持有人集中營","createTime":"2019-05-03T09:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T15:31:21.000Z","uid":98151,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8f620b448c23bebe1a148aeaa645adb127043452","tid":1136832,"uid":98151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:42:10.000Z","msg":"我地誠遨各位日日夜夜都上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9UP力特強，拎左白卡/就黎拎白卡/諗住拎白卡既痴線佬/婆入黎<br />\n<br />\n無乜選人要求，只有如下 :<br />\n1. 厹/娘娘收兵會先公開鞭屍唱通街再踢出谷<br />\n2. 太耐唔上水不定時就踢，無情講<br />\n3. 約左出谷聚但放飛機既都係公開鞭屍唱通街再踢出谷<br />\n<br />\n想識下朋友搵下飯腳既朋友仔 就請填以下表格再等入谷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(唔鍾意唔好填)<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScvai-Pra09d8vIym7hfQbGaJ-tEdzzhCXr7ZZnGR3xLUd9qg/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScvai-Pra09d8vIym7hfQbGaJ-tEdzzhCXr7ZZnGR3xLUd9qg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjBjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=7cb473ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScvai-Pra09d8vIym7hfQbGaJ-tEdzzhCXr7ZZnGR3xLUd9qg/viewform?usp=sf_link</a>"},{"pid":"cc333c253ccc1deb5c4541b202bbf92c8a292aba","tid":1136832,"uid":98151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ff0c13a8da4828f8f358d29e3cf1bb18a4a9e3","tid":1136832,"uid":98151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T16:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0523da0cbb96c3b24faa0e4437a9db0455f8a4","tid":1136832,"uid":98151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"